# Horizon Engine Audio Suite FH6 v1.0.0

## Download

Download the `.zip` file attached to this release.

## Highlights

- Exhaust presence refinement
- Intake response balancing
- Turbo spool and BOV behavior pass
- Backfire and anti-lag consistency tuning
- Engine-family progression improvements

## Install

1. Download the archive.
2. Extract it.
3. Read `INSTALL.txt`.
4. Back up original files.
5. Copy the package files into the matching location.

## Recommended asset name

```text
Horizon-Engine-Audio-Suite-FH6-v1.0.0.zip
```
